---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ISO Certified Quality | Amrich Pharma" description="Amrich Pharma's ISO-certified manufacturing, lab testing, and quality control for eco-safe aquaculture solutions.">
  <section class="hero-band-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>ISO-Certified Quality: Science You Can Trust</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm); max-width: 600px;">
        Every batch tested. Every formula validated. Every product built for Indian coastal conditions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-base); grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));">
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--semantic-up);">ISO 9001:2015</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">Quality Management Systems</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--semantic-up);">GMP Compliant</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">Good Manufacturing Practices</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
          <h3 style="color: var(--semantic-up);">Eco-Safe</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xs);">Biodegradable &amp; Low-Runoff</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Our Quality Process</h2>

      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-xl); display: grid; gap: var(--space-xl);">
        <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs);">
          <h3>1. Strain Selection &amp; R&amp;D</h3>
          <p>Microbial strains screened for efficacy across 5–65 ppt salinity, pH 6.5–10.0, and 5–45°C.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs);">
          <h3>2. Batch Testing &amp; CFU Validation</h3>
          <p>Every batch: &gt;1.2 billion CFU/g, purity, stability.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs);">
          <h3>3. Field Validation</h3>
          <p>Tested across AP, TN, Odisha, and Gujarat ponds.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: grid; gap: var(--space-xs);">
          <h3>4. Farmer Feedback Loop</h3>
          <p>Post-harvest data informs improvements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding surface-soft">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>What ISO 9001:2015 Means for You</h2>
      <ul style="margin-top: var(--space-sm); padding-left: var(--space-lg); display: grid; gap: var(--space-sm);">
        <li><strong>Consistency</strong> — Every batch meets the same high standard</li>
        <li><strong>Traceability</strong> — Full batch history from strain to shipment</li>
        <li><strong>Continuous Improvement</strong> — Processes refined quarterly</li>
        <li><strong>Documentation</strong> — Strict audit trails at every stage</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency</strong> — Batch reports available on request</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
      <h2>Interested in Dealer Opportunities?</h2>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        We partner with experienced aquaculture input dealers across coastal India. Contact us to learn about certification requirements, minimum order quantities, and territory availability.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Email: <a href="mailto:amrichpharma@gmail.com">amrichpharma@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding hero-band-dark" style="text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color: var(--on-dark);">Verify a Product Batch</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--on-dark-soft); margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
        Email your batch number for a detailed quality report
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:quality@amrichpharma.com" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: var(--space-lg); display: inline-flex;">
        quality@amrichpharma.com
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
